Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
Mario Maker Pumpkin Head Challenge ►► http://bit.ly/1I1HYkA

Here it is, the US PREMIER of Mario Party 3DS! If you've watched these streams before, you know I DOMINATE at Mario Party. We were pretty stoked to get a preview copy of the game, but you can't play Mario Party without, you know, a PARTY! So join me and Steph, Andre the Black Nerd, and RunJDRun for some SERIOUS Mario Partying.

RunJDRun: http://bit.ly/2bTnMLB
Black Nerd Comedy: http://bit.ly/1souUCL

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
